# Wiki Zone

This zone is managed by the `bcos-wiki` skill. Invoke it with `/wiki`.

Pages live in `pages/` for internal explanatory content and `source-summary/` for external captures. Raw source material lives under `raw/`. `index.md` is regenerated by `refresh_wiki_index.py`; `log.md` is append-only. See `docs/_bcos-framework/architecture/wiki-zone.md` for the full rules.
